::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer looks through the statuses of the protoforms, a bit bored. 
He leans forward as he comes to the one that was online and 
operational. DevilDuer smiles. That could mean more bots for the 
Alliance!

DevilDuer taps a few buttons on the console, cross-refrencing the 
number (Ax-426) to the list of known protoforms that the Iron Fist 
had in its databanks.
